This folder contains SPEC files for rpmbuild.

See rpmdev-setuptree for directory structure.

On Fedora, the default rpm build tree is ~/rpmbuild.

ls ~/rpmbuild 
BUILD/
BUILDROOT/
RPMS/
SOURCES/
SPECS/
SRPMS/

You can create this directory structure with rpmdev-setuptree from the rpmdevtools package.

(From: https://ro-che.info/articles/2018-01-25-rpm-packager-cheat-sheet)
